    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "# AI Ethics Roleplay\n\nYou and your group will evaluate the ethical use of computing system technologies through the viewpoint of different roles or personas.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7ed884a785962d36f729618a52716a2b-golden-stones-on-scales-on-marble-table-and-dark-b-2024-11-18-07-15-54-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-ae4d7072-fc5f-4cfa-9fb4-dd5c9540d2ea",
        "layout": "text-top-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Step 1 - Take on the role\n- Review the scenario with your group.\n- Understand the values and pressures of your assigned role.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7b093a027b5be78539d4069d92973e32-people-employees-icons-on-wooden-blocks-business-2024-10-11-02-59-12-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-96e1ca3b-ed52-4eaa-b731-18f40f537e1a",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Step 2 - Discuss\n- Answer the discussion questions from your role's perspective\n- Record main ideas, questions, and insights to digital sticky notes \n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/3bda10340cbe09f65232faea746eea8e-painted-light-bulb-with-word-idea-and-colored-blan-2023-11-27-05-17-12-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-3b8137d9-fcb7-43b7-8302-60cb3bf5ae98",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "# Step 3 - Propose a decision \n- Work with your group to create a proposal that addresses the scenario. \n- Your goal is to find a solution that feels fair to all roles.\n- Be ready to explain how your proposal considers each perspective.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/916cf5d643122f2099f30b6bec11aa74-balance-scale-placed-on-top-of-a-green-paper-cutou-2024-10-28-22-26-31-utc.jpg",
        "key": "computer-systems-lesson12-scenario-1-5babb39a-56a8-4610-bf06-154f025b2367"
      }
    ]
  },
